# Normalize line endings so Windows clones (with `core.autocrlf=true`)
# don't carry CRLF into the worktree. Without this, Biome's format gate
# (`lineEnding=lf`) trips on every Story-close pass and the framework's
# `npx biome format --write` autofix silently no-ops on Windows because
# `execFileSync` cannot resolve `npx.cmd` without `shell: true`.
#
# `text=auto eol=lf` tells Git to store text as LF and check it out as
# LF regardless of `core.autocrlf`. Binary files are left untouched.

* text=auto eol=lf
